2is for just uniform hinting types. 

3 

4This should only be used for types which are otherwise not native and would 

5require an import, including the typing module. The whole point of this is to 

6be a central collection of types for the purpose of type hinting. 

7 

8This module should never be used for anything other than hinting. Use proper 

9imports to access these classes. Otherwise, you will likely get circular  

10imports and other nasty things.
